schedule.pizza
==============

Open-source scheduling. Agent-native.

Share your URL. Visitors pick a time. Both calendars update.
Google Calendar only for now.

For N-person meetings, finds the best time for everyone. When
none exists, ranks alternatives by conflict severity and
suggests which flexible events to move.

API
---

::

    GET  /api/v1/availability?user={username}
    POST /api/v1/book
    GET  /api/v1

Development
-----------

::

    pnpm install
    pnpm dev
    pnpm build
    pnpm deploy

